Who We Are – Cidel













































Cidel

Toggle navigation



Cidel
Who We Are
What We Do
How We Do It
Current Thinking
 
Let’s Talk
Client Log In

 










We help high­ net worth individuals and families, legal and tax professionals, and some of the world’s largest institutions smartly structure, securely grow and easily manage wealth. It’s that simple. But naturally, there’s a lot more to say. 

Let’s start with our approach to wealth management:

 




						Our Approach						













								Everything is related.							

Your investment portfolio, real estate holdings, succession plans—all the pieces of your financial life form a single picture. Looking at the details as a whole is the only way to understand how they fit together. And it’s the best way to ensure your wealth stays sharply focused.




								Build on solid ground.							

When it comes to money, planning ahead and structuring with a purpose is always better than making things up as you go. Yes, it can take some initial effort, but a strong foundation lifts you closer to your ultimate goals. You’ll also sleep a lot better at night.




								Simplicity is the sharpest tool.							

The financial world is inherently complicated. With so many options and opportunities to consider it can be hard to see straight. Working creatively as a team, Cidel cuts through the clutter so our clients don’t have to.




								People make the difference.							

Numbers may be a central feature of the landscape, but real people and genuine relationships are what bring wealth management to life. From the beginning, Cidel has put its clients and colleagues first. It’s the way we like to do business and it’s the quickest path to results.




								If it doesn’t fit, then it’s not a solution.							

All of our clients are unique. They come to us with a broad range of needs and issues. So we don’t treat them like a herd. Instead, we go out of our way to customize solutions that are singularly perfect—for them.










						Our People						











			Leadership		

			Wealth Consultants		

			Investment Research		

			Planning, Structuring & Trust		



			Barbados		

			Canada		

			Latin America		

