Company Overview of Cidel Asset Management Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Cidel Asset Management Inc. is a privately owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to private and institutional clients, pension funds, foundations and endowments, insurance companies, sovereign and agency funds, and public mutual funds. It manages separate client-focused equity, fixed income, and balanced portfolios. The firm also manages mutual funds. It invests in the public equity markets of the world. The firm primarily invests in stocks of small-cap companies across diversified sectors. It employs combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis to create its portfolios. The firm conducts in-house research to make its investments. It was formerly known as Toron AMI...
Cidel Asset Management Inc. is a privately owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to private and institutional clients, pension funds, foundations and endowments, insurance companies, sovereign and agency funds, and public mutual funds. It manages separate client-focused equity, fixed income, and balanced portfolios. The firm also manages mutual funds. It invests in the public equity markets of the world. The firm primarily invests in stocks of small-cap companies across diversified sectors. It employs combination of fundamental and quantitative analysis to create its portfolios. The firm conducts in-house research to make its investments. It was formerly known as Toron AMI International Asset Management. The firm is based in Toronto, Canada with an additional office in Calgary, Canada. Cidel Asset Management Inc. operates as a subsidiary of Cidel Financial Group, Inc.
Detailed Description


