At Cidel Asset Management, we’ve built one of Canada’s more progressive investment management firms around a simple idea: partnership. Our team-driven, disciplined approach to investing globally and in Canada, along with superior service and open communication, leads to better outcomes for our clients. After all, that’s why our clients stay with us year after year.
Cidel is a global private banking group that offers a broad range of services and expertise. We manage the Toron AMI investment strategies that have benefitted our clients for over 50 years.
